The '''balloon city''' was the only permanent settlement of the [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] on [[Yibikkoror]], a planet in the [[Yinchorri system]]. The city's residents moved about using [[Yinchorri flutter-pack|flutter-packs]]. In [[33 BBY/Legends|33 BBY]], the city was the site of a [[Mission to Yibikkoror|battle]] between members of the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi Order]] and the Yinchorri, part of that year's [[Yinchorri Uprising]].

